title: High Elo Peoples
body:
Since is pre season, would any high elo care to invite me to play a game?
Im not sure how it works but i guess pre season wont effect to much?

I just think it would be a really awesome experience.
So if there is someone that wont mind, it would be really appreciated :)

ign- Avago Ya Mug

replies.body: Hate to tell you this but t he max rank you can duo with in ranked is gold 1
